module.exports={"en.pages":{"about":{"banner":"About A.D.U.","ourteam":"A.D.U. is a rapidly growing organization, and we bring together the most talented individuals from Niger and around the globe. If you share our values, believe that higher education can transform the Sahel region, and want to be part of that transformation and adventure, we want to talk with you. Have a look below to get some ideas as to ways to engage with A.D.U. If you are interested in one of these opportunities\u2014or something else\u2014please send us your CV and a cover note explaining your interest: ","title":{"1":"about","2":"Welcome","3":"Our Why","4":"Board of Trustees"},"values":{"h1":"Leadership","h2":"Excellence","h3":"Innovation","p1":"We believe that every problem is solvable when we commit the necessary time, creativity, energy, and grit. Every day, we search for better, more efficient ways to serve our community and we take personal responsibility for this.","p2":"We recognize that excellence is both technical and ethical and we take pride in our work. We strive to become a world-class institution. We never compromise on our values, and we never take short courts.","p3":"We consistently strive to find new ways to do better, to think out of the box, to use available local resources, and create models and solutions that have not been imagined or implemented yet."},"welcome":"Welcome by the Chacellor","why":{"btnLess":"view less","btnMore":"view more","p1":"The mission of A.D.U. is to prepare the most talented young people in Niger and in Francophone Africa to design and drive the development of their nations as ethical and effective leaders in the public, private and not-for-profit sectors.","p2":{"content":"We offer training in liberal arts that aims to develop students' critical thinking, problem-solving skills, and ability to serve their communities. A.D.U. is a bilingual institution (French and English) and is the first not-for-profit university in Niger to offer world-class education to students from the Sahel region. A.D.U. draws inspiration from the world's leading institutions of higher education such as Ashesi University in Ghana and Harvard University in the US. Founded in October 2017, A.D.U. has served a total of 250+ students of which 60% of our student population are female. From our initial student cohort (Obama Cohort), up to 90% of the entire student population, (now Alumni) are engaged in entrepreneurial ventures, working in fulltime jobs, as well as exploring graduate school opportunities."},"p3":"A.D.U. was established to address two of the most pressing problems facing the Sahel region i.e., the dearth of quality tertiary education institutions and the increasing cohort of young adults unprepared for participation and leadership in the 21st Century workforce. From inception to date, A.D.U. has played a leading role in changing the narrative that quality education is impossible to get most especially from the Sahel region of Africa. From an enrolment rate of 35 when we launched in 2017 to an enrolment rate of 524 in 2019, we have witnessed wide acceptance for our programs. We have also prioritized opening access to opportunities for young people, whereby 70% of our students receive some form of financial aid. This has enabled bright students from underserved communities to study at our institution, which was something that wouldn\u2019t have been erstwhile possible. \r\n              Our unique model \u2013 ILIMI; which means \u201ceducation, intellectual and knowledge\u201d in Hausa, focuses on developing ethical and impact driven young leaders."}},"academics":{"ac":"Academic Calendar","accounting":{"h1":"Bachelor of Accounting","p1":"A degree in Accounting and Finance will train you to work as a\r\n            financial examiner, or a financial analyst, or a finance manager or\r\n            as a business consultant who helps guide small entrepreneurs. It is\r\n            a very exacting work\u2026it requires a high level of attention to\r\n            detail.","p2":"<strong>Financial Examiner:<\/strong> With a career as a financial\r\n              examiner, you\u2019ll help ensure compliance with laws governing banks\r\n              and how they lend money, Or, you could be responsible for\r\n              analyzing the financial strength of a business that is looking to\r\n              expand.","p3":" <strong>Financial Analyst:<\/strong> You can expect to work with\r\n              individuals and organizations to make strategic decisions based on\r\n              investments","p4":"<strong>Business and Financial Consultant:<\/strong> As a business\r\n              consultant, you can help other business owners manage start-up\r\n              costs and investments, create a financial plan for their business\r\n              and monitor day-to-day bookkeeping."},"ai":"The Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence - BS(AI) program\r\n            provides learners the knowledge and skills to transform complex\r\n            inputs of text, vision, language and large databases into\r\n            intelligible and actionable decisions to enhance human capabilities.\r\n            The curriculum provides hands-on experience in various aspects of\r\n            Artificial Intelligence including data science, machine learning,\r\n            artificial neural networks, and developing data products. to address\r\n            societal and organisational issues in agriculture, commerce,\r\n            education, health, industry and governance etc.","aid":{"pp1":"<strong>Technology:<\/strong> Web and mobile software engineering,\r\n            computer architecture, databases, computer science theory.","pp2":"<strong>Data\/Analytics:<\/strong> Mathematics machine learning,\r\n            artificial neural networks, deep learning, and AI concepts and\r\n            software tools.","pp3":"<strong>Entrepreneurship:<\/strong> Innovation, strategy, problem\r\n            solving, management skills.","sh1":"Background","sh2":"Program Description","sh3":"Competencies & Skills","sp":"Niger 2.0 Smart Villages program was launched in August 2018 by the\r\n            Government of Niger and its partners (ITU, FAO, UNESCO, WHO, WB), to\r\n            expand internet access to digitally enabled services in education\r\n            and other sectors (health, agriculture, commerce etc.). Yet, there\r\n            is a lack of quality technology education programs in Niger and\r\n            across the Sahel region. Thus, the Bachelor of Science in Artificial\r\n            Intelligence (BS-AI) program is designed to bridge the\r\n            Science-Technology-Innovation (STI) workforce gap and to drive the\r\n            digital transformation agenda of Niger and the Sahel region.","sp1":"The Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence - BS(AI) program\r\n            provides learners the knowledge and skills to transform complex\r\n            inputs of text, vision, language and large databases into\r\n            intelligible and actionable decisions to enhance human capabilities.\r\n            222The curriculum provides hands-on experience in various aspects of\r\n            Artificial Intelligence including data science, machine learning,\r\n            artificial neural networks, and developing data products. to address\r\n            societal and organisational issues in agriculture, commerce,\r\n            education, health, industry and governance etc."},"banner":"A.D.U. offers 3-year liberal arts undergraduate programs; the only\r\n          university of its kind in the Sahel, and we hope to be a model that\r\n          other schools will follow. To further enhance the educational\r\n          experience, teaching at A.D.U. is split between on-the-ground faculty\r\n          who each have international education and experience, and top-tier\r\n          remote-based faculty from around the world.","ep":"The ADU English program is an English Learning establishment of the\r\n            African Development University that is focused on building the\r\n            English language proficiency of professionals, businessmen and\r\n            businesswomen etc., especially in the francophone region and is\r\n            committed to taking learners through an exciting language learning\r\n            journey with courses tailored to give learners an all-round study of\r\n            the language.","epd":{"ch1":"CERTIFICATE","cp":"A certificate of completion will be issued to students at the end\r\n              of every course taken in the English Program.","ph1":"OUR PACKAGES","pp1":"<strong>IN-CAMPUS PACKAGE:<\/strong> Classes on campus take place\r\n            every Tuesday and Thursday, 6:30pm.","pp2":"<strong>ONLINE PACKAGE:<\/strong> Virtual classes are offered based\r\n            on client\u2019s demand.","pp3":"<strong>COMPANY PACKAGE:<\/strong> This is for organizations who want\r\n            their staff to learn English.","pp4":"<strong>ENGLISH HUB PACKAGE:<\/strong> The English club holds every\r\n            Saturday by 4pm in our campus at Village de la Francophonie.","sh1":"COURSE SYLLABUS (What You will learn)","sp":"Our syllabus is comprised of topics in English grammar, vocabulary\r\n            and the four major language skills: listening, reading, writing,\r\n            speaking. Students will learn how to speak English with a higher\r\n            level of proficiency in both public speaking and normal English\r\n            conversations to help boost their communication skills."},"info":"For further information, please contact us via\r\n          <span>(+227)92 39 6868 \/93 39 6868<\/span> or you can also visit our\r\n          campus.","law":{"h1":"Bachelor of Business Law","p":"A.D.U. offers a three-year degree in Business Law that teaches\r\n            courses in many different aspects of legal work. Students entering\r\n            this program should have a strong commitment to justice and equality\r\n            and fighting corruption. The types of careers that graduates can\r\n            expect are Jurist of Enterprises, Magistrate in Public\r\n            Jurisdictions, Legal Consultant, Notary Public."},"link":{"1":"Business Management","2":"Artificial Intelligence","3":"English Programme"},"mis":{"h1":"Bachelor of Management Information System:","p1":"Information Technology is diverse. It will allow you to take your\r\n            profession in several different directions. It is practical. You\r\n            will not only learn the theory but also get the opportunity to make\r\n            things.","p3":"Technology positions available in IT often include jobs such as\r\n            creating software, analyzing new forms of data, and developing\r\n            solutions for today's highly technological world. In the next\r\n            ten-years Niger will be fully digital and nearly every company and\r\n            organization will be using digital technology. A.D.U.\u2019s program will\r\n            place you into the center of that exciting field by training you to\r\n            create new technologies. Security will also be in large demand,\r\n            people will want their mobiles and laptops to be secure from hackers\r\n            and from people trying to steal their personal information."},"pm":{"h1":"Bachelor of Project Management","p1":"Project Managers are trained to make certain that complex projects\r\n            go according to schedule. Project management positions are essential\r\n            in construction and civil engineering etc. These types of projects\r\n            include building new infrastructures such as bridges and office\r\n            buildings, as well as repairing old infrastructures, such as homes\r\n            or businesses.","p2":"In keeping with the Ilimi concept, each course is designed and\r\n            taught with a thread of ethical conduct woven through it to\r\n            reinforce the responsibility of graduates to press ethical practice\r\n            in their work-places. Courses also stress a commitment to combat\r\n            social injustice and to make the world a better place for the less\r\n            fortunate."},"rm":"Read More","title":{"1":"Business Administration (Featured Majors)","2":"Law","3":"Project Management","4":"Accounting","5":"Management Information System","6":"Artificial Intelligence","7":"English Programme"},"vfc":"View full calendar","vm":"View More"},"admission":{"advantage":{"1":"Student centered institution \u2013 Student FIRST","2":"US style Highee Education Model - liberal arts education","3":"International opportunities and exchange programs for students","4":"Entrepreneurial Focused","5":"Student Development Trough Experiential Learning","6":"Blended learning - in-person and virtual modes","7":"Bilingual education - English and French","8":"Effective career services and placement support"},"ap":{"link":{"cta":"Click to Apply","hta":"How to Apply","readMore":"Read More"},"p":"Our 3-year bachelor program is both nationally and internationally\r\n            recognized. Our degree programs are all accredited by Ministry of\r\n            Higher Education, Research and Innovation, Niger. We offer two\r\n            Bachelors: Business Administration & Artificial Intelligence."},"banner":"African Development University (A.D.U) is a university of excellence\r\n          based in Niamey (Niger). Our mission is to prepare the most talented\r\n          young people in Niger and Francophone Africa to design and drive the\r\n          development of their nations as ethical and effective leaders in\r\n          public, private and not for profit sectors.","cat":{"p":"For additional questions and\/or inquiry regarding application, you can\r\n          reach us through:"},"link":{"1":"The A.D.U Advantage","2":"Scholarship Information","3":"Academic Programs","4":"Contact Admission Team"},"si":{"apply":"Apply Now","link":{"1":"A.D.U. Scholarship","2":"MasterCard Foundation Scholarships"},"p1":"The mission of A.D.U. is to prepare the most talented young people\r\n            in Niger and in Francophone Africa to design and drive the\r\n            development of their nations as ethical and effective leaders in the\r\n            public, private and not-for-profit sectors.","p2":"Therefore, A.D.U. offers Scholarship for talented student who are\r\n            experiencing economic and social hardship so that they will be able\r\n            to achieve their goals and impact their community. You can apply for\r\n            a scholarship by filling this form."},"title":{"1":"admissions","2":"The A.D.U. Advantage","3":"Scholarship Information","4":"Academic Programs","5":"Contact Admission Team"}},"footer":{"ai":"Artificial Intelligence","ba":"Bachelor Admissions","email":"Email","ep":"English Program","phone":"Phone"},"home":{"banner":{"h1":"Changing the future","h2":"of the Sahel.","p":"ILIMI, African Development Universalis"},"me":"More Events","news":[{"images":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-4.jpg"],"text":"<p>A.D.U. was nominated, along with 3 other universities, as one of the best schools in the 8 regions of Niger.\r\nThe announcement was made at a grand gala held at the Mahatma Gandhi Conference Center on November 7, 2021\r\n<\/p><p>The Alkalami d'Or are trophies that reward public and private schools as well as universities and institutes in the eight regions of Niger for their willingness to make academic and extracurricular excellence their battle horse. At A.D.U. academic excellence reigns as evidenced by the 100% success rate in the Brevet de Techniciens Sup\u00e9rieur d'Etat in June 2021.<\/p>","title":"A.D.U. nominated as one of the  best Universities in Niger"},{"images":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-2.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-3.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-4.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-5.png"],"text":"\r\n        <p>On Friday, November 8 we received one of the funniest but also most inspiring visits. It was Oualas, one of the greatest African comedians, holder of the Best Comedian Award at the 1st edition of the Awards du Rire 2018.<\/p>\r\n        <p>Oualas, whose real name is Tahar Lazrak, came to visit us after his show at the Hotel Noom in Niamey, where A.D.U. was a partner. The joy and happiness of meeting the world star could be seen on the faces of the YoungLeaders who did not hesitate to take as many pictures as possible with Oualas, a.k.a the most Moroccan Ivorian of them all!<\/p>\r\n        ","title":"Oualas, one of Africa's greatest comedians visit A.D.U."},{"images":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-4.jpg"],"text":"\r\n        <p>On November 9th, during the Global Entrepreneurship Week, the iiLab, A.D.U.'s startup incubator, and the CIPMEN co-organized a training session called <q>Osez Entreprendre<\/q> (Dare to be entrepreneurial) for A.D.U.'s #YoungLeaders under the theme <q>Moringa Our Green Gold<\/q>.<\/p>\r\n        <p>During this training, they were given different notions to reinforce what they are already learning with iiLab. Right after the training, a visit to the CIPMEN premises took place with entrepreneurs coming from all over Niamey to exhibit products derived from Moringa. This was followed by a pitch competition where the candidate, Khadija Ibrahim, a 3rd year student at A.D.U. won first place!<\/p>\r\n        <p>The evening ended with a networking session around a buffet offered by the CIPMEN. A great way to celebrate the Global Entrepreneurship Week which starts on November 8th and ends on November 13th.<\/p>\r\n        ","title":"IILab and CIPMEN organise training for entrepreneurs"}],"partners":{"ashesi":{"link":"Visit Ashesi","name":"Ashesi University","p1":"With a ranking among the world's top 400 universities in the Times\r\n              Higher Education University Impact Rankings, in 2020, Ashesi\r\n              University is identified as one of the finest universities in\r\n              Africa.","p2":"From the begining to this day, A.D.U has been mentored and\r\n              supported by Ashesi, both, not-for-profit institutions and having\r\n              similar missions regarding raising the bar for higher education in\r\n              Africa by educating ethical and entrepreneurial leaders.","p3":"To fill the gap existing in higher education across the small\r\n              liberal arts colleges that are begining to establish in Africa,\r\n              Ashesi launched the Educative Collaboration, in which A.D.U. is\r\n              part of, in 2017."},"title":"Our Partners"},"programs":{"programs":[{"text":"The degree in Business Law teaches courses in many different\r\n                aspects of legal work, with a strong commitment to justice and\r\n                equality and fighting corruption.","title":"Law","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/law.jpg"},{"text":"The degree in Accounting and Finance will train you to work as a financial examiner, or a financial analyst, or as a business consultant who helps guide small entrepreneurs.","title":"Accounting & Finance","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/accounting.jpg"},{"text":"The degree in Project Management trains young leaders to manage and ensure that complex projects go according to schedule.","title":"Project Management","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/project.jpg"},{"text":"The degree in MIS will place you at the center of an exciting field by training you to create and manage new technologies.","title":"Management Information Systems","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/mis.jpg"},{"text":"The AI program equips young people with skills to develop intelligent systems and software that leverage data to solve societal and organizational issues.","title":"Artificial Intelligence","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/ai.jpg"},{"text":"The A.D.U. English program focuses on building the English language proficiency of students, professionals, and entreprenuers etc.","title":"English Program","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/english.png"}],"title":"Overview of Programs"},"rm":"Read More","studyAtADU":{"advantages":{"p11":"100%","p12":"Internships & Placement","p21":"70%","p22":"Scholarships & Financial Aid","p31":"70%","p32":"Women & Gender Equality"},"p":"African Development Universalis (A.D.U.) is a bilingual\r\n            establishment, with instruction in both French and English. We offer\r\n            fields of study within liberal arts framework for today\u2019s most\r\n            in-demand jobs, taught by committed professors who challenge you to\r\n            think critically and creatively. From interactive classes to\r\n            internship and research, you will transform as you pursue your\r\n            passions! Our unique model \u2013 ILIMI; which means \u201ceducation,\r\n            intellectual and knowledge\u201d in Hausa, focuses on developing ethical\r\n            and impact driven young leaders.","title":"Studying at A.D.U."},"va":"View all","values":{"1":"Leadership","2":"Innovation","3":"Excellence"},"vm":"View More","welcome":"Welcome to the Future"},"iilab":{"banner":"The iiLab (ilimi Innovation Lab) is A.D.U\u2019s innovation and\r\n            entrepreneurship hub committed to empowering our Young Leaders by\r\n            providing and connecting them with tools, resources, networks and\r\n            support to scale their innovative and entrepreneurial ideas.","events":[{"date":"September 14, 2021","description":"As lifelong members of the ilimi community, the iiLab\u2019s support to the Kagam\u00e9 cohort (which just graduated) will always be available. Nonetheless, for the upcoming months, the iiLab has an exciting and comprehensive entrepreneurship support program in store, just for the Kagam\u00e9 Cohort, made up of large-group sessions, one-on-one sessions, some funding, and other activities aiming to equip our Kagame Cohort Young Leaders with tools and resources for them to catalyze their growth as entrepreneurs and that of their ideas, regardless of their current advancement level. The Open House allowed the iiLab to give out more details about the program which will be informed by insights from a currently ongoing needs-assessment process.\r\n                    Note: The iiLab also has exciting plans for the Wangari, Johnson and Jean cohorts, once they return to campus.","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/5.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/6.jpeg"],"title":"iiLab Open House for the Kagam\u00e9 cohort"},{"date":"November 20, 2021","description":"In their latest newsletter issue, Ashesi University, our mentor and partner, featured the iiLab, our ILIMI INNOVATION LAB, where our #ADUYoungLeaders express their entrepreneurial creativity.\nThe article narrates how our super star Fey\u00e7al managed to create his business thanks to the iiLab support over the years, despite all the constraints faced by young entrepreneurs in Niger.\nThe focus was on the fact that A.D.U. intends to become a model for universities in the Sahel wanting to implement transformative start-up incubators. Indeed, given the enormous potential of entrepreneurship in the future we want for Niger and the Sahel in general, the development of the entrepreneurial skills of our Young Leaders as well as that of their initiatives has always had a central place in A.D.U.\u2019s learning model.","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/5.jpeg"],"title":"Feature by Ashesi University via the Education Collaborative Newsletter"},{"date":"December 05, 2021","description":"In collaboration with E-Takara, the iiLab of A.D.U held an info session yesterday on the A.D.U campus. We were privileged to have previous laureates of the competition such as Latifa Salissou Hassane (via audio recording), Rafiou Ala Roi Fhad (in person) and Idriss Laouali Abdou (via video-recording) share with ADU Young Leaders about the incredible experience their participation in the competition has been for them. The E-Takara team also shared more about the vision behind the competition, as well as the selection criteria, before encouraging A.D.U Young Leaders to apply massively.","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/4.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/5.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/6.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/7.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/8.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/9.jpg"],"title":"In collaboration with E-TAKARA"}],"link":{"1":"About iiLab","2":"Services","3":"Events","4":"Our Entrepreneures","5":"Spotlight"},"me":"More Events","rm":"Read More","services":{"card":{"1":"A.D.U. Young Leader support services","2":"Business\/ Professional development","3":"Coaching","4":"Funding","5":"Mentorship","6":"Exposure to external opportunities for our Young Leaders","7":"Research ","8":"Entrepreneurship incubator "},"text":"Career Services \u2013 is a unit within Student and Community Affairs, which provides career readiness and preparation to our young leaders. The goal of career services is to provide career assistance for students in their career choices and help them to find work-study positions, internships and full-time positions upon graduation. The Career Services organizes workshops, provides career counseling and assists students with a variety of career development needs. \r\nThis office focuses on employer relations at the national and international level to provide employment opportunities for current students and alumni.\r\n","title":"SERVICES"},"showrooms":[{"description":"Tallit Design is a new company aiming to promote African and mainly Nigerien culture through the making of accessories for men and women and clothing combining modernity and culture. Tallit Design is also in the field of interior design and events, highlighting African cultures, using our various traditional loincloths. To date, Tallit has had to participate in several events and organized its very first fashion show for the launch of its collection named Mahba. Thanks to the success of such a fashion show, Tallit Design had the privilege to dress the hostesses during the opening ceremony of King Abdullah bin Abdulaziz Al Saoud University, organized by the Waqf authority, among other opportunities. Do not hesitate to contact them at 89257766 or via their email address tallitdesign227@gmail.com and follow them on","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/5.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/6.jpeg"],"title":"Aichatou Mahamane (Kagame Cohort): CEO of Tallit Design"},{"description":"Kakaki is an agency specializing in global business communication. We do all kinds of design, printing on any medium, embroidery, personalized advertising gadgets, business flyers, community management etc. Kakaki is also involved in major communication projects such as branding of buildings, vehicles, illuminated signs, totems, 3D illuminated initials, painting, etc. The very first companies to trust our services are (among others) EBTP Grand Projet (for which we crafted golden initials, and community management), SOPAMIN (for their new website), Le SULTAN (for their totem and community management), Polyclinic Magori (we branding their cars, sewing their blouses, digital embroidery, goodies, etc.), ADU (for kakemonos, photo frames, and others), Nikki Hotel (for their luminous initials), ETS Zaao (for their luminous initials and t-shirts), and Guimbia make-up (for their luminous initials). For all your communication needs, do not hesitate to contact them at 91912329\/89417277, or via their email address contactkakaki@gmail.com \/ souleymanemsani@gmail.com. You can follow them on","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/4.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/5.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/6.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/7.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/8.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/9.jpg"],"title":"Mahaman Sani A. Souleymane (Obama Cohort): CEO of Kakaki Multimedia"},{"description":"Sahel Solar Academy is a non-profit technical and vocational training institution on the various installation and maintenance techniques of solar power plants as well as underground water pumps powered by PV. It is a center where people will come to learn how to install and maintain PV powered power plants, solar panels and underground water pumps in households, businesses, communities, villages and any particular place it either commercial, industrial, institutional or residential.","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/5.jpeg"],"title":"Abdoul-Rachid Maman Kadade (Kagame Cohort): CEO of Sahel Solar Academy"}],"title":{"1":"iiLab","2":"Welcome to IILab"},"va":"View all","vm":"View More","welcome":"The iiLab (ilimi Innovation Lab) is A.D.U\u2019s innovation and\r\n            entrepreneurship hub committed to empowering our Young Leaders by\r\n            providing and connecting them with tools, resources, networks and\r\n            support to scale their innovative and entrepreneurial ideas."},"navigation":{"1":"About","2":"Study","3":"IILab","4":"Student Life","5":"Apply","6":"Enquire","7":"Donate"},"studentLife":{"banner":"Student life typically involves social activities within the A.D.U. campus, and the time spent with school-mates and teachers within the class and outside. The goal of student life is to create a good environment where students will grow and have a very good experience during their academic journey at A.D.U.","link":{"1":"Life on Campus","2":"Spotlight"},"me":"More Events","rm":"Read More","title":{"1":"Student Life","2":"LIFE ON CAMPUS","3":"ilimi Student Government","4":"Internship and Career Services","5":"Clubs and Societies","6":"Guest Lecture Series","7":"Health and Well-being","8":"Student Success Center","9":"Alumni","10":"STUDENT SPOTLIGHT","11":"SPIRIT OF GIVING CROWD FUNDING"},"va":"View all","vm":"View More"},"studyatadu":{"admission":{"admissions":[{"text":"You must have a Baccalaureate certificate; High School Final Exam Grades, Birth Certificate, Certificate of Citizenship, Language test scores and Letters of Recommendation.","title":"Requirements","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/requirement.jpg"},{"text":"To apply, visit our online application portal to create an account, fill out the application form, upload all required documents, pay the registration fee, and submit your application.","title":"Apply Online","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/apply-online.jpg"},{"text":"A.D.U. offers Scholarship for talented student who are experiencing economic and social hardship so that they will be able to achieve their goals and impact their community.","title":"Scholarship","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/scholarship.jpg"},{"text":"For additional questions and\/or inquiry regarding the status of your application, you can reach us through:\nadmissions@ilimi.edu.ne,\n+227 923 968 68 (WhatsApp)\n+227 9339 68 68 (Mobile)","title":"Contact Admissions","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/contact.jpg"}],"cta":{"text":"Our 3-year bachelor programs are both nationally and internationally recognized. Our degree programs are all accredited by Ministry of Higher Education, Research and Innovation, Niger.  Apply to Study with us!","title":"Admissions"},"title":"Become a Young Leader"},"advantages":{"p11":"100%","p12":"Student","p13":"Centered","p21":"100%","p22":"Entrepreneurial","p23":"Focused","p31":"70%","p32":"Bilingual Education","p33":"English & French"},"ai":{"background":{"p":"The UN recognizes the role of technology, science and capacity building as major pillars of the means of implementing and achieving the SDGs. Globally, the Industry 4.0 revolution requires young people to acquire and maintain digital skills for innovation & entrepreneurship. Furthermore, the Niger 2.0 strategic plan seeks to employ digital technologies to promote the development of Niger, by focusing on four strategic areas: e-government, digital skills promotion, a smart villages program and creating an innovation and technology city. Thus, the Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence (BS-AI) program is designed to bridge the Science-Technology-Innovation (STI) workforce gap and to drive the digital transformation agenda of Niger and the Sahel region.","title":"Background"},"description":{"p":"The Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence - BS(AI) program provides learners the knowledge and skills to transform complex inputs of text, vision, language and large databases into intelligible and actionable decisions to enhance human capabilities. The curriculum provides hands-on experience in various aspects of Artificial Intelligence including foundations of data science, artificial intelligence languages, machine learning, artificial neural networks, and developing data products backed with strong foundations of software engineering for web and mobile, agile principles, ethics and social theory. The program will equip students with skills in computational thinking, problem modelling, software engineering and project management to develop data-driven intelligent systems and software to address societal and organisational issues in agriculture, commerce, education, health, industry and governance etc.","title":"Program Description"},"outcomes":{"p":{"1":"Leverage the principles computing with emphasis on Artificial Intelligence to address issues in areas like health, education, commerce and agriculture etc.","2":"Transform complex inputs, such as vision, language, and other databases, into intelligent and actionable decisions","3":"Solve applications and systems software challenges with a comprehensive set of software engineering skills in desktop, web and mobile","4":"Apply leadership and ethical principles in solving societal and organizational problems using AI"},"title":"Outcomes"},"title":" Artificial Intelligence"},"banner":"Study at A.D.U.","ep":{"background":{"p":"The ADU English program is an English Learning establishment of the African Development University that is focused on building the English language proficiency of professionals, businessmen and businesswomen etc., especially in the francophone region and is committed to taking learners through an exciting language learning journey with courses tailored to give learners an all-round study of the language. A mastery of English language helps you to easily navigate through the business environment, to communicate effectively in English Language, collaborate effectively with English speaking colleagues, business partners and prospective business partners from English speaking countries and to increase your chances of getting jobs and expanding your net worth and network as a bilingual speaker.","title":"Background"},"cs":{"p":"Our syllabus is comprised of topics in English grammar, vocabulary and the four major language skills: listening, reading, writing, speaking. Our courses are delivered using the following methods: Teacher-led mode of instruction; Student-led mode of teaching: using debates, oral and written presentations etc. and Instructional video and audio materials.\\Students will take a placement test at the beginning of the program to determine their current proficiency level and at the end of the program, there will also be another placement test to review their growth rate. The current levels we have are Beginner (A1), Pre-intermediate (A2), Intermediate (B1) and High-intermediate (B2)","title":"Course Syllabus"},"packages":{"p":{"a":"<strong>On-Campus Package:<\/strong> We are located at Village de la Francophonie where our physical classes are held. Classes on campus take place every Tuesday and Thursday, 6:30pm.","b":"<strong>Company Package:<\/strong> We also have a learning package for companies and organizations who want members of their staff to learn English. Our teachers are available to come to your companies and teach based on the schedule that works for you. The only requirement for this package is for a class to have a minimum of 10 students\/learners."},"title":"Our Packages"},"title":"English Program"},"majors":{"accounting":{"p1":"A degree in Accounting and Finance will train you to work as a financial examiner, or a financial analyst, or a finance manager or as a business consultant who helps guide small entrepreneurs. It is a very exacting work\u2026it requires a high level of attention to detail.","p2":"A degree in accounting can give you the skills you need to work as a business and financial consultant, helping entrepreneurs and small business owners find financial success. With a career as a financial examiner, you\u2019ll help ensure compliance with laws governing banks and how they lend money.","title":"Bachelor of Accounting"},"law":{"p1":"A.D.U. offers a three-year degree in Business Law that teaches courses in many different aspects of legal work. Students entering this program should have a strong commitment to justice and equality and fighting corruption.","p2":"The types of careers that graduates can expect are Jurist of Enterprises, Magistrate in Public Jurisdictions, Legal Consultant, Notary Public. Our courses are taught by a diverse body of professionals who bring a rich international background to the ADU campus.","title":"Bachelor of Business Law"},"mis":{"p1":"Information Technology processes rely on creativity & problem-solving. Studying IT will provide you with an opportunity to use your skills to come up with innovative solutions to problems faced by the world.","p2":"Technology positions available in IT often include jobs such as creating software, analyzing new forms of data, and developing solutions for today's highly technological world. A.D.U.\u2019s program will place you into the center of that exciting field by training you to create new technologies.","title":"Bachelor of Management Information Systems"},"pm":{"p1":"Project Managers are trained to make certain that complex projects go according to schedule. Project management positions are essential in construction and civil engineering etc. Large Humanitarian Assistance Organizations such as UNHCR, WFP and international NGOs often employ many project managers to help maintain efficiency within the day-to-day tasks of the organization.","p2":"In keeping with the Ilimi concept, each course is designed and taught with a thread of ethical conduct woven through it to reinforce the responsibility of graduates to press ethical practice in their work-places. Courses also stress a commitment to combat social injustice and to make the world a better place for the less fortunate","title":"Bachelor of Project Management"},"title":"Business Administration (Featured Majors)"},"p":"African Development University (A.D.U) is a university of excellence based in Niamey (Niger). A.D.U draws inspiration from the world\u2019s leading institutions of higher education such as Ashesi University in Ghana and Harvard University in the US. A.D.U is a bilingual establishment, with instruction in both French and English.","title":"The A.D.U. Advantage"}},"fr.pages":{"about":{"banner":"About A.D.U.","ourteam":"A.D.U. est une organisation en croissance rapide, et nous rassemblons les individus les plus talentueux du Niger et du monde entier. Si vous partagez nos valeurs, croyez que l'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur peut transformer la r\u00e9gion du Sahel et souhaitez faire partie de cette transformation et de cette aventure, nous voulons parler avec vous. Jetez un \u0153il ci-dessous pour avoir quelques id\u00e9es sur les moyens de vous engager avec A.D.U. Si l'une de ces opportunit\u00e9s ou autre vous int\u00e9resse, veuillez nous envoyer votre CV et une note de motivation expliquant votre int\u00e9r\u00eat : ","title":{"1":"\u00c0 propos","2":"Bienvenue \u00e0 ilimi","3":"Notre Pourquoi","4":"Direction"},"values":{"h1":"Leadership","h2":"Excellence","h3":"Innovation","p1":"Nous croyons que chaque probl\u00e8me peut \u00eatre r\u00e9solu lorsque nous consacrons le temps, la cr\u00e9ativit\u00e9, l'\u00e9nergie et le courage n\u00e9cessaires. Chaque jour, nous recherchons des moyens meilleurs et plus efficaces de servir notre communaut\u00e9 et nous en assumons personnellement la responsabilit\u00e9.","p2":"L'excellence est \u00e0 la fois technique et \u00e9thique. Nous sommes fiers de notre travail. Nous nous effor\u00e7ons de devenir une institution de classe mondiale. Nous ne transigeons jamais sur nos valeurs et nous ne prenons jamais de raccourcis.","p3":"Nous nous effor\u00e7ons constamment de trouver de nouvelles fa\u00e7ons de faire mieux, de sortir des sentiers battus, d'utiliser les ressources locales disponibles et de cr\u00e9er des mod\u00e8les et des solutions qui n'ont pas encore \u00e9t\u00e9 imagin\u00e9s ou mis en \u0153uvre."},"welcome":"Welcome by the Chacellor","why":{"btnLess":"voir moins","btnMore":"voir plus","p1":"L'Universit\u00e9 Africaine de D\u00e9veloppement (ADU) est une universit\u00e9 innovante \u00e0 but non lucratif dont la mission est de pr\u00e9parer les jeunes les plus talentueux du Niger et d'Afrique francophone \u00e0 concevoir et conduire le d\u00e9veloppement de leurs nations en tant que leaders \u00e9thiques et efficaces dans les secteurs public, priv\u00e9 et les secteurs \u00e0 but non lucratif. A.D.U. est la premi\u00e8re universit\u00e9 \u00e0 but non lucratif situ\u00e9e \u00e0 Niamey, au Niger, et est la premi\u00e8re institution \u00e0 offrir une \u00e9ducation de classe mondiale aux \u00e9tudiants de la r\u00e9gion du Sahel.","p2":{"content":"Fond\u00e9e en Octobre 2017, A.D.U. propose actuellement des programmes de premier cycle accr\u00e9dit\u00e9s par le minist\u00e8re de la Recherche, de l'Enseignement sup\u00e9rieur et de l'Innovation du Niger, un programme de MBA, ainsi que des cours pour cadres. Au cours de la d\u00e9cennie suivante, A.D.U. aspire \u00e0 devenir la plaque tournante de l'innovation et de l'excellence dans l'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur en Afrique de l'Ouest.\r\nA.D.U. a \u00e9t\u00e9 cr\u00e9\u00e9 pour r\u00e9soudre deux des probl\u00e8mes les plus urgents auxquels la r\u00e9gion est confront\u00e9e :\r\n","l1":"La p\u00e9nurie d'\u00e9tablissements d'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur de qualit\u00e9.","l2":"La masse croissante de jeunes adultes non pr\u00e9par\u00e9s \u00e0 la participation et au leadership dans la main-d'\u0153uvre du 21e si\u00e8cle."},"p3":"Le Niger est un pays en croissance rapide de 20 millions d'habitants, et notre d\u00e9sir de former une nouvelle g\u00e9n\u00e9ration de leaders qualifi\u00e9s et \u00e9thiques est motiv\u00e9 par notre engagement \u00e0 faire progresser le d\u00e9veloppement du Niger et \u00e0 am\u00e9liorer le niveau de vie de tous. En fin de compte, \u00e0 travers notre travail, nous visons \u00e0 faire progresser la qualit\u00e9 du capital humain des pays du Sahel et du continent africain."}},"academics":{"ac":"Calendrier acad\u00e9mique","accounting":{"h1":"Licence en comptabilit\u00e9","p1":"Un dipl\u00f4me en comptabilit\u00e9 et finance vous formera pour travailler comme examinateur financier, ou analyste financier, ou directeur financier ou comme consultant en affaires qui aide \u00e0 guider les petits entrepreneurs. C'est un travail tr\u00e8s exigeant... il n\u00e9cessite une grande attention aux d\u00e9tails.","p2":"<strong>Examinateur Financier:<\/strong> Dans le cadre d'une carri\u00e8re d'examinateur financier, vous contribuerez \u00e0 assurer le respect des lois r\u00e9gissant les banques et la fa\u00e7on dont elles pr\u00eatent de l'argent, ou vous pourriez \u00eatre charg\u00e9 d'analyser la solidit\u00e9 financi\u00e8re d'une entreprise qui cherche \u00e0 se d\u00e9velopper.","p3":"<strong>Analyste Financier:<\/strong> Vous pouvez vous attendre \u00e0 travailler avec des individus et des organisations pour prendre des d\u00e9cisions strat\u00e9giques bas\u00e9es sur des investissements.","p4":"<strong>Consultant en entreprises et en finances:<\/strong> Un dipl\u00f4me en comptabilit\u00e9 peut vous donner les comp\u00e9tences n\u00e9cessaires pour travailler comme consultant en entreprises et en finances, en aidant les entrepreneurs et les propri\u00e9taires de petites entreprises \u00e0 trouver la r\u00e9ussite financi\u00e8re. En tant que consultant en affaires, vous pouvez aider d'autres propri\u00e9taires d'entreprises \u00e0 g\u00e9rer les co\u00fbts de d\u00e9marrage et les investissements, \u00e0 cr\u00e9er un plan financier pour leur entreprise et \u00e0 surveiller la tenue des livres au jour le jour."},"ai":"Le programme Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence - BS(AI) fournit aux apprenants les connaissances et les comp\u00e9tences n\u00e9cessaires pour transformer des entr\u00e9es complexes de texte, de vision, de langage et de grandes bases de donn\u00e9es en d\u00e9cisions intelligibles et exploitables pour am\u00e9liorer les capacit\u00e9s humaines. Le programme donnera aux \u00e9tudiants des comp\u00e9tences en mati\u00e8re de pens\u00e9e informatique, de mod\u00e9lisation des probl\u00e8mes, de g\u00e9nie logiciel et de gestion de projet pour d\u00e9velopper des syst\u00e8mes et des logiciels intelligents ax\u00e9s sur les donn\u00e9es afin de r\u00e9pondre aux probl\u00e8mes soci\u00e9taux et organisationnels dans les domaines de l'agriculture, du commerce, de l'\u00e9ducation, de la sant\u00e9, de l'industrie et de la gouvernance, etc.","aid":{"pp1":"<strong>La technologie:<\/strong> G\u00e9nie logiciel web et mobile, architecture informatique, bases de donn\u00e9es, th\u00e9orie informatique.","pp2":"<strong>Analyse des donn\u00e9es:<\/strong> Apprentissage automatique des math\u00e9matiques, r\u00e9seaux de neurones artificiels, apprentissage en profondeur et concepts et outils logiciels d'IA.","pp3":"<strong>Entrepreneuriat:<\/strong> Innovation, strat\u00e9gie, r\u00e9solution de probl\u00e8mes, comp\u00e9tences en gestion.","sh1":"Fond","sh2":"Description du programme","sh3":"Comp\u00e9tences et aptitudes","sp":"Le programme Niger 2.0 Smart Villages a \u00e9t\u00e9 lanc\u00e9 en ao\u00fbt 2018 par le gouvernement nig\u00e9rien et ses partenaires (UIT, FAO, UNESCO, OMS, BM), afin d'\u00e9tendre l'acc\u00e8s \u00e0 Internet \u00e0 des services activ\u00e9s par le num\u00e9rique dans l'\u00e9ducation et d'autres secteurs (sant\u00e9, agriculture, commerce, etc.). Pourtant, il y a un manque de programmes d'\u00e9ducation technologique de qualit\u00e9 au Niger et dans toute la r\u00e9gion du Sahel. Il y a donc un manque de main-d'\u0153uvre qualifi\u00e9e en science, technologie et innovation (STI) pour conduire la transformation num\u00e9rique du pays. Il en r\u00e9sulte une faible production (services et applications num\u00e9riques) n\u00e9cessaire \u00e0 l'\u00e9conomie num\u00e9rique par rapport au reste du monde. Ainsi, le programme Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence (BS-AI) est con\u00e7u pour combler le d\u00e9ficit de main-d'\u0153uvre en science-technologie-innovation (STI) et pour conduire l'agenda de transformation num\u00e9rique du Niger et de la r\u00e9gion du Sahel.","sp1":"Le programme Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence - BS(AI) fournit aux apprenants les connaissances et les comp\u00e9tences n\u00e9cessaires pour transformer des entr\u00e9es complexes de texte, de vision, de langage et de grandes bases de donn\u00e9es en d\u00e9cisions intelligibles et exploitables pour am\u00e9liorer les capacit\u00e9s humaines.\r\nLe programme d'\u00e9tudes fournit une exp\u00e9rience pratique dans divers aspects de l'intelligence artificielle, y compris les fondements de la science des donn\u00e9es, les langages d'intelligence artificielle, l'apprentissage automatique, les r\u00e9seaux neuronaux artificiels et le d\u00e9veloppement de produits de donn\u00e9es soutenus par de solides bases de g\u00e9nie logiciel pour le web et le mobile, les principes agiles, l'\u00e9thique et la th\u00e9orie sociale.\r\nLe programme donnera aux \u00e9tudiants des comp\u00e9tences en mati\u00e8re de pens\u00e9e informatique, de mod\u00e9lisation des probl\u00e8mes, de g\u00e9nie logiciel et de gestion de projet pour d\u00e9velopper des syst\u00e8mes et des logiciels intelligents ax\u00e9s sur les donn\u00e9es afin de r\u00e9pondre aux probl\u00e8mes soci\u00e9taux et organisationnels dans les domaines de l'agriculture, du commerce, de l'\u00e9ducation, de la sant\u00e9, de l'industrie et de la gouvernance, etc.\r\n"},"banner":"A.D.U. propose des programmes de premier cycle en arts lib\u00e9raux de 3 ans; la seule universit\u00e9 de ce type au Sahel, et nous esp\u00e9rons \u00eatre un mod\u00e8le que d'autres \u00e9coles suivront. Pour am\u00e9liorer encore l'exp\u00e9rience \u00e9ducative, l'enseignement \u00e0 A.D.U. est divis\u00e9 entre des professeurs sur le terrain qui ont chacun une formation et une exp\u00e9rience internationales, et des professeurs \u00e0 distance de premier plan du monde entier.","ep":"Le programme d'anglais ADU est un \u00e9tablissement d'apprentissage de l'anglais de l'Universit\u00e9 africaine de d\u00e9veloppement qui se concentre sur le renforcement des comp\u00e9tences en anglais des professionnels, des hommes d'affaires et des femmes d'affaires, etc., en particulier dans la r\u00e9gion francophone et s'engage \u00e0 accompagner les apprenants dans un voyage d'apprentissage linguistique passionnant avec des cours adapt\u00e9s pour donner aux apprenants une \u00e9tude compl\u00e8te de la langue.","epd":{"ch1":"CERTIFICAT","cp":"Un certificat d'ach\u00e8vement sera d\u00e9livr\u00e9 aux \u00e9tudiants \u00e0 la fin\r\nde chaque cours suivi dans le programme d'anglais.","ph1":"NOS FORFAITS","pp1":"<strong>FORFAIT SUR LE CAMPUS:<\/strong> Les cours sur le campus ont lieu tous les mardis et jeudis \u00e0 18h30.","pp2":"<strong>FORFAIT EN LIGNE:<\/strong> Les cours virtuels sont offerts en fonction de la demande du client.","pp3":"<strong>FORFAIT ENTREPRISE:<\/strong> C'est pour les organisations qui veulent que leur personnel apprenne l'anglais.","pp4":"<strong>FORFAIT HUB ANGLAIS:<\/strong> Le club anglais se tient tous les samedis \u00e0 16h dans notre campus du Village de la Francophonie.","sh1":"PROGRAMME DE COURS (Ce que vous apprendrez)","sp":"Notre programme comprend des sujets sur la grammaire anglaise, le vocabulaire et les quatre principales comp\u00e9tences linguistiques : \u00e9couter, lire, \u00e9crire, parler. Les \u00e9tudiants apprendront \u00e0 parler anglais avec un niveau plus \u00e9lev\u00e9 de ma\u00eetrise de la parole en public et des conversations en anglais normal pour aider \u00e0 renforcer leurs comp\u00e9tences en communication."},"info":"Pour plus d'informations, veuillez nous contacter via\r\n          <span>(+227)92 39 6868 \/93 39 6868<\/span> ou vous pouvez \u00e9galement visiter notre campus.","law":{"h1":"Licence en droit des affaires ","p":"A.D.U. offre un dipl\u00f4me de trois ans en droit des affaires qui dispense des cours sur de nombreux aspects diff\u00e9rents du travail juridique. Les \u00e9tudiants qui s'inscrivent \u00e0 ce programme doivent avoir un fort engagement envers la justice et l'\u00e9galit\u00e9 et la lutte contre la corruption. Les types de carri\u00e8res auxquels les dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s peuvent s'attendre sont les suivants : juriste d'entreprise, magistrat dans les juridictions publiques, consultant juridique, notaire public."},"link":{"1":"Gestion d'entreprise","2":"Intelligence artificielle","3":"Programme d'anglais"},"mis":{"h1":"Licence en syst\u00e8me d'information de gestion:","p1":"La technologie de l'information est diversifi\u00e9e. Elle vous permettra d'orienter votre profession dans plusieurs directions diff\u00e9rentes. Elle est pratique. Vous n'apprendrez pas seulement la th\u00e9orie, mais aurez aussi l'occasion de faire des choses.","p2":"Les \u00e9tudes d'informatique offrent de nombreuses possibilit\u00e9s de carri\u00e8re. \u00c0 mesure que la technologie progresse, le besoin de dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s en informatique ne fera qu'augmenter. En outre, plus vos comp\u00e9tences seront \u00e9lev\u00e9es, plus vous serez demand\u00e9.","p3":"Les postes disponibles en informatique comprennent souvent des emplois tels que la cr\u00e9ation de logiciels, l'analyse de nouvelles formes de donn\u00e9es et l'\u00e9laboration de solutions pour le monde hautement technologique d'aujourd'hui. Dans les dix prochaines ann\u00e9es, le Niger sera enti\u00e8rement digitalis\u00e9 et presque toutes les entreprises et organisations utiliseront la technologie digitale. Le programme d'A.D.U. vous placera au centre de ce domaine passionnant en vous formant \u00e0 la cr\u00e9ation de nouvelles technologies. La s\u00e9curit\u00e9 sera \u00e9galement tr\u00e8s demand\u00e9e, les gens voudront que leurs portables et ordinateurs portables soient prot\u00e9g\u00e9s contre les pirates informatiques et les personnes qui tentent de voler leurs informations personnelles."},"pm":{"h1":"Licence en gestion de projet","p1":"Les gestionnaires de projet sont form\u00e9s pour s'assurer que les projets complexes se d\u00e9roulent conform\u00e9ment au calendrier. Les postes de gestion de projet sont essentiels dans la construction, le g\u00e9nie civil, etc. Ces types de projets comprennent la construction de nouvelles infrastructures telles que des ponts et des immeubles de bureaux, ainsi que la r\u00e9paration d'anciennes infrastructures, comme des maisons ou des entreprises.","p2":"Conform\u00e9ment au concept Ilimi, chaque cours est con\u00e7u et enseign\u00e9 avec un fil conducteur de conduite \u00e9thique afin de renforcer la responsabilit\u00e9 des dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s \u00e0 faire pression sur les pratiques \u00e9thiques sur leur lieu de travail. Les cours mettent \u00e9galement l'accent sur l'engagement \u00e0 combattre l'injustice sociale et \u00e0 faire du monde un endroit meilleur pour les moins fortun\u00e9s."},"rm":"Lire la suite","title":{"1":"Administration des affaires (Majeures en vedette)","2":"Droit","3":"Gestion d'entreprise","4":"Comptabilit\u00e9","5":"Systeme d'Information de gestion","6":"Intelligence artificielle","7":"Programme d'anglais"},"vfc":"Voir le calendrier complet","vm":"Voir plus"},"admission":{"advantage":{"1":"Une institution centr\u00e9e sur le bien-\u00eatre et le succ\u00e8s de nos \u00e9tudiants \u2013 Notre credo c\u2019est \u00ab\u202fL\u2019\u00e9tudiant d\u2019abord!","2":"Un mod\u00e8le d'Enseignement Sup\u00e9rieur \u00e0 l'Am\u00e9ricaine","3":"Un cadre de formation en arts lib\u00e9raux\u202f: un mod\u00e8le \u00e9ducatif qui d\u00e9veloppe des capacit\u00e9s telles que la r\u00e9solution de probl\u00e8mes, la libert\u00e9 de choix, une vaste palette de connaissances et des comp\u00e9tences transf\u00e9rables (polyvalence)","4":"Une institution centr\u00e9e sur l'entrepreneuriat","5":"Un d\u00e9veloppement des \u00e9tudiants \u00e0 travers l'apprentissage par l'exp\u00e9rience\u202f: d\u00e9velopper le leadership, les relations, les comp\u00e9tences de vie, les comp\u00e9tences sociales et \u00e9motionnelles et la curiosit\u00e9 intellectuelle de nos \u00e9tudiants","6":"Apprentissage mixte\u202f: une combinaison d'enseignement et d'apprentissage en pr\u00e9sentiels et virtuels","7":"\u00c9ducation et environnement du campus bilingue (anglais et fran\u00e7ais)","8":"Un service \u00ab\u202fCarri\u00e8re\u202f\u00bb de haut niveau d\u00e9di\u00e9 pour accompagner nos \u00e9tudiants dans la vie active"},"ap":{"link":{"cta":"Cliquez pour postuler","hta":"Comment s'inscrire","readMore":"Lire la suite"},"p":"Notre Licence (cursus de 3 ans) est reconnue \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9chelle nationale et internationale. Tous nos dipl\u00f4mes sont accr\u00e9dit\u00e9s par le Minist\u00e8re de l\u2019Enseignement Sup\u00e9rieur, de la Recherche et de l\u2019Innovation du Niger.  \r\n              Nous proposons deux dipl\u00f4mes de Licence: Business Administration & Artificial Intelligence."},"banner":"African Development Universalis (A.D.U) est une universit\u00e9 d\u2019excellence bas\u00e9e \u00e0 Niamey (NIGER). Notre mission est de fournir une formation exceptionnelle de haut niveau afin de pr\u00e9parer les jeunes les plus prometteurs du Niger \u2013 et de l\u2019Afrique en g\u00e9n\u00e9rale - \u00e0 mener un leadership \u00e9thique dans les secteurs public, priv\u00e9 et \u00e0 but non lucratif.","cat":{"p":"Pour toutes questions suppl\u00e9mentaires et\/ou des demandes de renseignements concernant l'avancement de votre demande, vous pouvez nous joindre via:"},"link":{"1":"L'Avantage A.D.U","2":"Informations sur la bourse","3":"R\u00e9sum\u00e9 des programmes acad\u00e9miques","4":"Contactez notre \u00e9quipe  Admissions"},"si":{"apply":"Appliquer maintenant","link":{"1":"A.D.U. Bourse d'\u00e9tudes","2":"Bourses de la Fondation MasterCard"},"p1":"La mission d'A.D.U. est de pr\u00e9parer les jeunes les plus talentueux du Niger et de l'Afrique francophone \u00e0 concevoir et \u00e0 conduire le d\u00e9veloppement de leurs nations en tant que leaders \u00e9thiques et efficaces dans les secteurs public, priv\u00e9 et \u00e0 but non lucratif.","p2":"Par cons\u00e9quent, A.D.U. offre des bourses d'\u00e9tudes aux \u00e9tudiants talentueux qui connaissent des difficult\u00e9s \u00e9conomiques et sociales afin qu'ils puissent atteindre leurs objectifs et avoir un impact sur leur communaut\u00e9.\r\nVous pouvez demander une bourse d'\u00e9tudes en remplissant le formulaire suivant"},"title":{"1":"admissions","2":"L'Avantage A.D.U","3":"Informations sur la bourse","4":"R\u00e9sum\u00e9 des programmes acad\u00e9miques","5":"Contactez notre \u00e9quipe  Admissions"}},"footer":{"ai":"Intelligence artificielle","ba":"Admissions au baccalaur\u00e9at","email":"Courriel","ep":"Programme d'anglais","phone":"T\u00e9l\u00e9phone"},"home":{"banner":{"h1":"Changer l'avenir","h2":"du Sahel.","p":"ILIMI, African Development Universalis"},"me":"Plus d'\u00e9v\u00e9nements","news":[{"images":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-4.jpg"],"text":"<p>A.D.U. a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9sign\u00e9, avec 3 autres universit\u00e9s, comme l'une des meilleures \u00e9coles des 8 r\u00e9gions du Niger.\r\nL'annonce a \u00e9t\u00e9 faite lors d'un grand gala organis\u00e9 au centre de conf\u00e9rence Mahatma Gandhi le 7 novembre 2021.\r\n<\/p><p>Les Alkalami d'Or sont des troph\u00e9es qui r\u00e9compensent les \u00e9coles publiques et priv\u00e9es ainsi que les universit\u00e9s et instituts des huit r\u00e9gions du Niger pour leur volont\u00e9 de faire de l'excellence acad\u00e9mique et parascolaire leur cheval de bataille. \u00c0 'A.D.U. l'excellence acad\u00e9mique r\u00e8gne comme en t\u00e9moigne le taux de r\u00e9ussite de 100% au Brevet de Techniciens Sup\u00e9rieur d'Etat en juin 2021.<\/p>","title":"L'A.D.U. d\u00e9sign\u00e9e comme l'une des meilleures universit\u00e9s du Niger"},{"images":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-2.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-3.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-4.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-5.png"],"text":"\r\n        <p>Vendredi 8 novembre, nous avons re\u00e7u l'une des visites les plus dr\u00f4les mais aussi les plus inspirantes. Il s'agissait de Oualas, l'un des plus grands humoristes africains, d\u00e9tenteur du prix du meilleur humoriste lors de la 1\u00e8re \u00e9dition des Awards du Rire 2018.<\/p>\r\n        <p>Oualas, de son vrai nom Tahar Lazrak, est venu nous rendre visite apr\u00e8s son spectacle \u00e0 l'h\u00f4tel Noom de Niamey, o\u00f9 A.D.U. \u00e9tait partenaire. La joie et le bonheur de rencontrer la star mondiale se lisaient sur les visages des YoungLeaders qui n'ont pas h\u00e9sit\u00e9 \u00e0 prendre un maximum de photos avec Oualas, alias le plus marocain des Ivoiriens !<\/p>\r\n        ","title":"Oualas, l'un des plus grands humoristes africains en visite \u00e0 l'A.D.U."},{"images":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-4.jpg"],"text":"\r\n        <p>Le 9 novembre, pendant la semaine mondiale de l'entrepreneuriat, l'iiLab, l'incubateur de startups de l'A.D.U., et le CIPMEN ont co-organis\u00e9 une session de formation intitul\u00e9e <q>Osez Entreprendre<\/q> pour les #YoungLeaders de l'A.D.U. sous le th\u00e8me <q>Moringa Our Green Gold<\/q>.<\/p>\r\n        <p>Pendant cette formation, diff\u00e9rentes notions leur ont \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9es pour renforcer ce qu'ils apprennent d\u00e9j\u00e0 avec iiLab. Juste apr\u00e8s la formation, une visite des locaux du CIPMEN a eu lieu avec des entrepreneurs venus de tout Niamey pour exposer des produits d\u00e9riv\u00e9s du Moringa. Cette visite a \u00e9t\u00e9 suivie d'un concours de pitch o\u00f9 la candidate, Khadija Ibrahim, \u00e9tudiante en 3\u00e8me ann\u00e9e \u00e0 l'A.D.U. a remport\u00e9 la premi\u00e8re place !<\/p>\r\n        <p>La soir\u00e9e s'est termin\u00e9e par une session de networking autour d'un buffet offert par le CIPMEN. Une belle fa\u00e7on de c\u00e9l\u00e9brer la Semaine mondiale de l'entrepreneuriat qui d\u00e9bute le 8 novembre et se termine le 13 novembre.<\/p>\r\n        ","title":"IILab et CIPMEN organisent une formation pour les entrepreneurs"}],"partners":{"ashesi":{"link":"Visitez Ashesi","name":"Ashesi University","p1":"Avec un classement parmi les 400 meilleures universit\u00e9s du monde dans le classement Times Higher Education University Impact Rankings, en 2020, l'Universit\u00e9 Ashesi est reconnue comme \u00e9tant l'une des meilleures universit\u00e9s d'Afrique.","p2":"De ses d\u00e9buts \u00e0 ce jour, A.D.U a \u00e9t\u00e9 encadr\u00e9 et soutenu par Ashesi, tous deux \u00e9tant des institutions \u00e0 but non lucratif et ayant des missions similaire quand \u00e0 l'\u00e9l\u00e9vation de la barre dans l'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur en Afrique \u00e0 travers la formation de leaders \u00e9thiques et entrepreneuriaux.","p3":"En 2017, Ashesi lance la collaboration \u00e9ducative, dans laquelle A.D.U fait partie, pour combler le vide existant dans l'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur au sein du petit groupe d'universit\u00e9s d'arts lib\u00e9raux qui commencent \u00e0 s'\u00e9tablir en Afrique."},"title":"Nos partenaires"},"programs":{"programs":[{"text":"A.D.U. offre un dipl\u00f4me de trois ans en droit des affaires qui dispense des cours sur de nombreux aspects diff\u00e9rents du travail juridique.","title":"Droit","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/law.jpg"},{"text":"Un dipl\u00f4me en comptabilit\u00e9 et finance vous formera pour travailler comme analyste financier, ou comme consultant en affaires qui aide \u00e0 guider les petits entrepreneurs.","title":"Comptabilit\u00e9","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/accounting.jpg"},{"text":"Les gestionnaires de projet sont form\u00e9s pour s'assurer que les projets complexes se d\u00e9roulent conform\u00e9ment au calendrier.","title":"Gestion de projet","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/project.jpg"},{"text":"Le programme d'A.D.U. vous placera au centre de ce domaine passionnant en vous formant \u00e0 la cr\u00e9ation de nouvelles technologies","title":"Informatique de Gestion (SI)","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/mis.jpg"},{"text":"Le programme dote les jeunes de comp\u00e9tences pour d\u00e9velopper des syst\u00e8mes et des logiciels intelligents qui exploitent les donn\u00e9es pour r\u00e9soudre les probl\u00e8mes soci\u00e9taux et organisationnels.","title":"Intelligence Artificielle","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/ai.jpg"},{"text":"Le programme d'anglais de l'A.D.U. vise \u00e0 renforcer les comp\u00e9tences en anglais des \u00e9tudiants, des professionnels, des entrepreneurs, etc.","title":"English Program","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/english.png"}],"title":"Aper\u00e7u des programmes"},"rm":"Lire la suite","studyAtADU":{"advantages":{"p11":"100%","p12":"Stages & placements","p21":"70%","p22":"Bourses d'\u00e9tudes\n& aide financi\u00e8re","p31":"70%","p32":"Femmes & \u00e9galit\u00e9 des sexes"},"p":"African Development Universalis A.D.U est un \u00e9tablissement bilingue et offre \u00e0 ses \u00e9tudiants une formation en arts lib\u00e9raux, les rendant aptes \u00e0 occuper avec succ\u00e8s les emplois les plus demand\u00e9s. Ces formations sont dispens\u00e9es par des professeurs engag\u00e9s qui vous mettent au d\u00e9fi et vous incite \u00e0 penser de mani\u00e8re critique et cr\u00e9ative afin de trouver des solutions aux probl\u00e9matiques de votre communaut\u00e9. Que ce soit en groupes de cours intensifs, durant vos stages, ou en faisant de la recherche, \u00e0 A.D.U vous vous transformerez tout en vivant vos passions!","title":"\u00c9tudier \u00e0 l'A.D.U."},"va":"Voir tout","values":{"1":"Leadership","2":"Innovation","3":"Excellence"},"vm":"Voir plus","welcome":"Bienvenue dans le futur"},"iilab":{"banner":"Le iiLab (ilimi Innovation Lab) est le p\u00f4le d'innovation et d'entrepreneuriat d'A.D.U qui s'engage \u00e0 responsabiliser nos jeunes leaders en leur fournissant et en leur fournissant des outils, des ressources, des r\u00e9seaux et un soutien pour d\u00e9velopper leurs id\u00e9es innovantes et entrepreneuriales.","events":[{"date":"Septembre 14, 2021","description":"En tant que membres \u00e0 vie de la communaut\u00e9 ilimi, le soutien de l'iiLab \u00e0 la cohorte Kagam\u00e9 (qui vient d'\u00eatre dipl\u00f4m\u00e9e) sera toujours disponible. N\u00e9anmoins, pour les mois \u00e0 venir, le iiLab a en r\u00e9serve un programme passionnant et complet de soutien \u00e0 l'entrepreneuriat, juste pour la cohorte Kagam\u00e9, compos\u00e9 de sessions en groupe, de sessions individuelles, de financement et d'autres activit\u00e9s visant \u00e0 \u00e9quiper nos jeunes leaders de la cohorte Kagame avec des outils et des ressources leur permettant de catalyser leur croissance en tant qu'entrepreneurs et celle de leurs id\u00e9es, quel que soit leur niveau d'avancement actuel. La journ\u00e9e portes ouvertes a permis au iiLab de donner plus de d\u00e9tails sur le programme \u00e0 venir pour la cohorte Kagam\u00e9.\r\nRemarque : Le iiLab a \u00e9galement des initiatives en vue pour les cohortes Wangari, Johnson et Jean, une fois qu'elles seront de retour sur le campus.\r\n","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/5.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/6.jpeg"],"title":"Journ\u00e9e de portes ouvertes du iiLab pour la cohorte Kagam\u00e9"},{"date":"Novembre 20, 2021","description":"Dans leur newsletter de ce mois, Ashesi University, notre mentor et partenaire de tous les jours, \u00e0 parl\u00e9 du iiLab, notre ILIMI INNOVATION LAB, l\u00e0 o\u00f9 toute la cr\u00e9ativit\u00e9 entrepreneuriale de nos #ADUYoungLeaders est concentr\u00e9e.\nIl a \u00e9t\u00e9 question de voir comment notre super star Fey\u00e7al \u00e0 su cr\u00e9er son entreprise malgr\u00e9 toutes les contraintes qui se pr\u00e9sentent aux jeunes entrepreneurs du Niger.\nIl a surtout \u00e9t\u00e9 question du fait que le iiLab de A.D.U. sera \u00e0 l\u2019avenir un centre de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence pour les universit\u00e9s qui veulent impl\u00e9menter le syst\u00e8me d\u2019incubateur de starts-up. En effet, vu le potentiel \u00e9norme de l'entreprenariat dans le futur que nous voulons pour le Niger et le Sahel en g\u00e9n\u00e9ral, le d\u00e9veloppement des aptitudes entrepreneuriales de nos Young Leaders ainsi que celui de leurs initiatives \u00e0 toujours eu une place centrale dans le mod\u00e8le \u00e9ducatif de A.D.U.","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/5.jpeg"],"title":"Le iiLab dans la Newsletter du Education Collaborative "},{"date":"Decembre 05, 2021","description":"Nous avons eu le privil\u00e8ge d'avoir des anciens laur\u00e9ats du concours tels que Latifa Salissou Hassane (via un enregistrement audio), Rafiou Ala Roi Fhad (en personne) et Idriss Laouali Abdou (via un enregistrement vid\u00e9o) qui ont partag\u00e9 avec les Young Leaders d'A.D.U. l'exp\u00e9rience incroyable que leur participation au concours a \u00e9t\u00e9 pour eux. \r\nL'\u00e9quipe d'e-Takara a \u00e9galement expliqu\u00e9 la vision qui sous-tend le concours, ainsi que les crit\u00e8res de s\u00e9lection, avant d'encourager nos Young Leaders a postuler massivement.\r\n","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/4.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/5.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/6.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/7.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/8.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/9.jpg"],"title":"En collaboration avec E-TAKARA"}],"link":{"1":"\u00c0 propos de iiLab","2":"Prestations de service","3":"\u00c9v\u00e9nements","4":"Nos Entrepreneurs","5":"Projecteur"},"me":"Plus d'\u00e9v\u00e9nements","rm":"Lire la suite","services":{"card":{"1":"A.D.U. Services d'accompagnement des jeunes leaders","2":"D\u00e9veloppement commercial\/professionnel","3":"Encadrement","4":"Le financement","5":"Mentorat","6":"Exposition \u00e0 des opportunit\u00e9s externes pour nos jeunes leaders","7":"Recherche","8":"Incubateur d'entrepreneuriat"},"text":"Les services d'orientation professionnelle sont une unit\u00e9 des affaires \u00e9tudiantes et communautaires qui pr\u00e9pare et pr\u00e9pare nos jeunes leaders \u00e0 la carri\u00e8re. L'objectif des services de carri\u00e8re est de fournir une assistance aux \u00e9tudiants dans leur choix de carri\u00e8re et de les aider \u00e0 trouver des postes en alternance, des stages et des postes \u00e0 temps plein apr\u00e8s l'obtention de leur dipl\u00f4me. Le service des carri\u00e8res organise des ateliers, fournit des conseils en mati\u00e8re de carri\u00e8re et aide les \u00e9tudiants \u00e0 r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 divers besoins en mati\u00e8re de d\u00e9veloppement de carri\u00e8re. \r\nCe bureau se concentre sur les relations avec les employeurs au niveau national et international afin d'offrir des opportunit\u00e9s d'emploi aux \u00e9tudiants actuels et aux anciens \u00e9tudiants.\r\n","title":"PRESTATIONS DE SERVICE"},"showrooms":[{"description":"Tallit Design est une nouvelle entreprise qui a pour but de promouvoir la culture africaine et principalement nig\u00e9rienne \u00e0 travers la confection d'accessoires pour hommes et femmes et l'habillement alliant modernit\u00e9 et culture. L\u2019entreprise Tallit Design se veut \u00e9galement innovante dans le domaine de la d\u00e9coration d'int\u00e9rieur et de l'\u00e9v\u00e9nementiel, tout en mettant en avant nos cultures, en utilisant nos diff\u00e9rents pagnes traditionnels. A ce jour, Tallit a eu \u00e0 participer \u00e0 plusieurs \u00e9v\u00e9nements et \u00e0 organiser son tout premier d\u00e9fil\u00e9 pour le lancement de sa collection d'habits nomm\u00e9e Mahba. Gr\u00e2ce au succ\u00e8s de ce d\u00e9fil\u00e9, Tallit Design \u00e0 eu le privil\u00e8ge d\u2019assurer l'habillement des h\u00f4tesses lors de l'inauguration de l'universit\u00e9 du Roi Abdullah bin Abdulaziz Al Saoud, organis\u00e9 par la haute autorit\u00e9 Waqf, parmi d\u2019autres opportunit\u00e9s. N'h\u00e9sitez pas \u00e0 les contacter au 89257766 ou via leur adresse email tallitdesign227@gmail.com et suivez les sur","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/5.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/shoe\/6.jpeg"],"social":["Facebook: tallit design","Instagram: tallitforculture","Twitter: tallit design","LinkedIn: tallit design"],"title":"Aichatou Mahamane (Kagame Cohort): CEO de Tallit Design"},{"description":"Kakaki est une agence sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9e dans la communication globale des entreprises. Nous faisons toute sorte de Conception, l'impression sur tout support, la broderie, les gadgets publicitaires personnalis\u00e9s, les prospectus d'entreprises, le community management etc. Kakaki est aussi impliqu\u00e9 dans les grands travaux de communication tels que le branding de b\u00e2timent, de v\u00e9hicules, les enseignes lumineuses, les totems, les lettrines lumineuses 3D, la peinture, etc. Les toutes premi\u00e8res entreprises nous ayant fait confiance sont entre autres EBTP Grand Projet (\u00e0 qui nous avons fait des lettrines dor\u00e9e, et le community management), SOPAMIN (pour le nouveau site internet), Le SULTAN (pour le totem et le community management), Polyclinique Magori (pour le branding des voitures, la couture de blouse et broderie num\u00e9rique, les goodies, etc.), A.D.U. (pour les kak\u00e9monos, cadres photos, et autres), Nikki Hotel (pour les lettrines lumineuses), ETS Zaao (pour les lettrines lumineuses et tee-shirt), et Guimbia make-up (pour les lettrines lumineuses). Pour tous vos besoins en communication, n'h\u00e9sitez pas \u00e0 les contacter au 91912329 \/ 89417277, ou via leur adresse email contactkakaki@gmail.com \/ souleymanemsani@gmail.com. Vous pouvez les suivre sur","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/4.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/5.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/6.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/7.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/8.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/cosm\/9.jpg"],"social":["Facebook: kakaki multimedia","Instagram: kakakimultimedia","Twitter: kakaki multimedia"],"title":"Mahaman Sani A. Souleymane (Obama Cohort): CEO de Kakaki Multimedia"},{"description":"Sahel Solar Academy est une institution \u00e0 but non lucratif de formation technique et professionnelle sur les diff\u00e9rentes techniques d'installation et de maintenance des centrales solaires mais aussi des pompes \u00e0 eau souterraines aliment\u00e9es par PV. C'est un centre o\u00f9 les gens viendront apprendre \u00e0 installer et \u00e0 entretenir des centrales \u00e9lectriques, des panneaux solaires et des pompes \u00e0 eau souterraines aliment\u00e9es par PV dans les m\u00e9nages, les entreprises, les communaut\u00e9s, les villages et tout endroit particulier qu'il soit commercial, industriel, institutionnel ou r\u00e9sidentiel.","images":["\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/1.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/2.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/3.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/4.jpeg","\/storage\/pages\/iilab\/bike\/5.jpeg"],"social":[],"title":"Abdoul-Rachid Maman Kadade (Kagame Cohort): CEO de Sahel Solar Academy"}],"title":{"1":"iiLab","2":"Bienvenue \u00e0 IILab"},"va":"Voir tout","vm":"Voir plus","welcome":"Le iiLab (ilimi Innovation Lab) est le p\u00f4le d'innovation et d'entrepreneuriat d'A.D.U qui s'engage \u00e0 responsabiliser nos jeunes leaders en leur fournissant et en leur fournissant des outils, des ressources, des r\u00e9seaux et un soutien pour d\u00e9velopper leurs id\u00e9es innovantes et entrepreneuriales."},"navigation":{"1":"\u00c0 propos","2":"\u00c9tude","3":"IILab","4":"Vie \u00e9tudiante","5":"Appliquer","6":"Renseigner","7":"Faire un don"},"studentLife":{"banner":"La vie \u00e9tudiante implique g\u00e9n\u00e9ralement des activit\u00e9s sociales au sein de l'A.D.U. campus, et le temps pass\u00e9 avec les camarades de classe et les enseignants au sein de la classe et \u00e0 l'ext\u00e9rieur. Le but de la vie \u00e9tudiante est de cr\u00e9er un bon environnement o\u00f9 les \u00e9tudiants grandiront et auront une tr\u00e8s bonne exp\u00e9rience au cours de leur parcours acad\u00e9mique \u00e0 A.D.U.","link":{"1":"La vie sur le campus","2":"Projecteur"},"me":"Plus d'\u00e9v\u00e9nements","rm":"Lire la suite","title":{"1":"Vie \u00e9tudiante","2":"LA VIE SUR LE CAMPUS","3":"Gouvernement \u00e9tudiant ilimi","4":"Services de stages et de carri\u00e8re","5":"Clubs et associations","6":"S\u00e9rie de conf\u00e9rences invit\u00e9es","7":"Sant\u00e9 et bien-\u00eatre","8":"Centre de r\u00e9ussite des \u00e9tudiants","9":"Anciens","10":"PLEINS FEUX SUR LES \u00c9TUDIANTS","11":"L'ESPRIT DE DONNER UN FINANCEMENT COLLECTIF"},"va":"Voir tout","vm":"Voir plus"},"studyAtAdu":{"banner":{"h1":"Changer l'avenir","h2":"du Sahel.","p":"ILIMI, African Development Universalis"},"me":"Plus d'\u00e9v\u00e9nements","news":[{"image":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-a-4.jpg"],"text":"<p>A.D.U. a \u00e9t\u00e9 d\u00e9sign\u00e9, avec 3 autres universit\u00e9s, comme l'une des meilleures \u00e9coles des 8 r\u00e9gions du Niger.\r\nL'annonce a \u00e9t\u00e9 faite lors d'un grand gala organis\u00e9 au centre de conf\u00e9rence Mahatma Gandhi le 7 novembre 2021.\r\n<\/p><p>Les Alkalami d'Or sont des troph\u00e9es qui r\u00e9compensent les \u00e9coles publiques et priv\u00e9es ainsi que les universit\u00e9s et instituts des huit r\u00e9gions du Niger pour leur volont\u00e9 de faire de l'excellence acad\u00e9mique et parascolaire leur cheval de bataille. \u00c0 'A.D.U. l'excellence acad\u00e9mique r\u00e8gne comme en t\u00e9moigne le taux de r\u00e9ussite de 100% au Brevet de Techniciens Sup\u00e9rieur d'Etat en juin 2021.<\/p>","title":"L'A.D.U. d\u00e9sign\u00e9e comme l'une des meilleures universit\u00e9s du Niger"},{"image":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-2.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-3.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-4.png","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-b-5.png"],"text":"\r\n        <p>Vendredi 8 novembre, nous avons re\u00e7u l'une des visites les plus dr\u00f4les mais aussi les plus inspirantes. Il s'agissait de Oualas, l'un des plus grands humoristes africains, d\u00e9tenteur du prix du meilleur humoriste lors de la 1\u00e8re \u00e9dition des Awards du Rire 2018.<\/p>\r\n        <p>Oualas, de son vrai nom Tahar Lazrak, est venu nous rendre visite apr\u00e8s son spectacle \u00e0 l'h\u00f4tel Noom de Niamey, o\u00f9 A.D.U. \u00e9tait partenaire. La joie et le bonheur de rencontrer la star mondiale se lisaient sur les visages des YoungLeaders qui n'ont pas h\u00e9sit\u00e9 \u00e0 prendre un maximum de photos avec Oualas, alias le plus marocain des Ivoiriens !<\/p>\r\n        ","title":"Oualas, l'un des plus grands humoristes africains en visite \u00e0 l'A.D.U."},{"image":["\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-1.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-2.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-3.jpg","\/storage\/pages\/home\/news\/news-c-4.jpg"],"text":"\r\n        <p>Le 9 novembre, pendant la semaine mondiale de l'entrepreneuriat, l'iiLab, l'incubateur de startups de l'A.D.U., et le CIPMEN ont co-organis\u00e9 une session de formation intitul\u00e9e <q>Osez Entreprendre<\/q> pour les #YoungLeaders de l'A.D.U. sous le th\u00e8me <q>Moringa Our Green Gold<\/q>.<\/p>\r\n        <p>Pendant cette formation, diff\u00e9rentes notions leur ont \u00e9t\u00e9 donn\u00e9es pour renforcer ce qu'ils apprennent d\u00e9j\u00e0 avec iiLab. Juste apr\u00e8s la formation, une visite des locaux du CIPMEN a eu lieu avec des entrepreneurs venus de tout Niamey pour exposer des produits d\u00e9riv\u00e9s du Moringa. Cette visite a \u00e9t\u00e9 suivie d'un concours de pitch o\u00f9 la candidate, Khadija Ibrahim, \u00e9tudiante en 3\u00e8me ann\u00e9e \u00e0 l'A.D.U. a remport\u00e9 la premi\u00e8re place !<\/p>\r\n        <p>La soir\u00e9e s'est termin\u00e9e par une session de networking autour d'un buffet offert par le CIPMEN. Une belle fa\u00e7on de c\u00e9l\u00e9brer la Semaine mondiale de l'entrepreneuriat qui d\u00e9bute le 8 novembre et se termine le 13 novembre.<\/p>\r\n        ","title":"IILab et CIPMEN organisent une formation pour les entrepreneurs"}],"partners":{"ashesi":{"link":"Visitez Ashesi","name":"Ashesi University","p1":"Avec un classement parmi les 400 meilleures universit\u00e9s du monde dans le classement Times Higher Education University Impact Rankings, en 2020, l'Universit\u00e9 Ashesi est reconnue comme \u00e9tant l'une des meilleures universit\u00e9s d'Afrique.","p2":"De ses d\u00e9buts \u00e0 ce jour, A.D.U a \u00e9t\u00e9 encadr\u00e9 et soutenu par Ashesi, tous deux \u00e9tant des institutions \u00e0 but non lucratif et ayant des missions similaire quand \u00e0 l'\u00e9l\u00e9vation de la barre dans l'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur en Afrique \u00e0 travers la formation de leaders \u00e9thiques et entrepreneuriaux.","p3":"En 2017, Ashesi lance la collaboration \u00e9ducative, dans laquelle A.D.U fait partie, pour combler le vide existant dans l'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur au sein du petit groupe d'universit\u00e9s d'arts lib\u00e9raux qui commencent \u00e0 s'\u00e9tablir en Afrique."},"title":"Nos partenaires"},"programs":{"programs":[{"text":"A.D.U. offre un dipl\u00f4me de trois ans en droit des affaires qui dispense des cours sur de nombreux aspects diff\u00e9rents du travail juridique.","title":"Droit","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/law.jpg"},{"text":"Un dipl\u00f4me en comptabilit\u00e9 et finance vous formera pour travailler comme analyste financier, ou comme consultant en affaires qui aide \u00e0 guider les petits entrepreneurs.","title":"Comptabilit\u00e9","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/accounting.jpg"},{"text":"Les gestionnaires de projet sont form\u00e9s pour s'assurer que les projets complexes se d\u00e9roulent conform\u00e9ment au calendrier.","title":"Gestion de projet","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/project.jpg"},{"text":"Le programme d'A.D.U. vous placera au centre de ce domaine passionnant en vous formant \u00e0 la cr\u00e9ation de nouvelles technologies","title":"Informatique de Gestion (SI)","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/mis.jpg"},{"text":"Le programme dote les jeunes de comp\u00e9tences pour d\u00e9velopper des syst\u00e8mes et des logiciels intelligents qui exploitent les donn\u00e9es pour r\u00e9soudre les probl\u00e8mes soci\u00e9taux et organisationnels.","title":"Intelligence Artificielle","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/ai.jpg"},{"text":"Le programme d'anglais de l'A.D.U. vise \u00e0 renforcer les comp\u00e9tences en anglais des \u00e9tudiants, des professionnels, des entrepreneurs, etc.","title":"English Program","url":"\/storage\/pages\/home\/programs\/english.png"}],"title":"Aper\u00e7u des programmes"},"rm":"Lire la suite","studyAtADU":{"advantages":{"p11":"100%","p12":"Stages & placements","p21":"70%","p22":"Bourses d'\u00e9tudes\n& aide financi\u00e8re","p31":"70%","p32":"Femmes & \u00e9galit\u00e9 des sexes"},"p":"African Development Universalis A.D.U est un \u00e9tablissement bilingue et offre \u00e0 ses \u00e9tudiants une formation en arts lib\u00e9raux, les rendant aptes \u00e0 occuper avec succ\u00e8s les emplois les plus demand\u00e9s. Ces formations sont dispens\u00e9es par des professeurs engag\u00e9s qui vous mettent au d\u00e9fi et vous incite \u00e0 penser de mani\u00e8re critique et cr\u00e9ative afin de trouver des solutions aux probl\u00e9matiques de votre communaut\u00e9. Que ce soit en groupes de cours intensifs, durant vos stages, ou en faisant de la recherche, \u00e0 A.D.U vous vous transformerez tout en vivant vos passions!","title":"\u00c9tudier \u00e0 l'A.D.U."},"va":"Voir tout","vm":"Voir plus","welcome":"Bienvenue dans le futur"},"studyatadu":{"admission":{"admissions":[{"text":"Vous devez \u00eatre en possession d'un certificat de baccalaur\u00e9at, des notes de l'examen final du lyc\u00e9e, d'un certificat de naissance, d'un certificat de citoyennet\u00e9, des r\u00e9sultats des tests de langue et de lettres de recommandation.","title":"Exigences","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/requirement.jpg"},{"text":"Pour postuler, visitez notre portail de candidature en ligne pour cr\u00e9er un compte, remplir le formulaire de candidature, t\u00e9l\u00e9charger tous les documents requis, payer les frais d'inscription et soumettre votre candidature.","title":"Postuler en ligne","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/apply-online.jpg"},{"text":"A.D.U. offre des bourses d'\u00e9tudes aux \u00e9tudiants talentueux qui connaissent des difficult\u00e9s \u00e9conomiques et sociales afin qu'ils puissent atteindre leurs objectifs et avoir un impact sur leur communaut\u00e9.","title":"Bourse d'\u00e9tudes","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/scholarship.jpg"},{"text":"Pour toute question suppl\u00e9mentaire et\/ou demande de renseignements concernant l'\u00e9tat de votre demande, vous pouvez nous joindre \u00e0 l'adresse suivante:\nadmissions@ilimi.edu.ne,\n+227 923 968 68 (WhatsApp)\n+227 9339 68 68 (Mobile)","title":"Contacter les admissions","url":"\/storage\/pages\/academics\/contact.jpg"}],"cta":{"text":"Nos programmes de licence en trois ans sont reconnus au niveau national et international. Nos programmes sont tous accr\u00e9dit\u00e9s par le Minist\u00e8re de l'Enseignement Sup\u00e9rieur, de la Recherche et de l'Innovation du Niger.  Postulez pour \u00e9tudier avec nous !","title":"Admissions"},"title":"Devenir un jeune Leader"},"advantages":{"p11":"100%","p12":"\u00c9tudiant","p13":"Centr\u00e9","p21":"100%","p22":"Entrepreneuriat","p23":"Focalis\u00e9","p31":"70%","p32":"L'\u00e9ducation bilingue","p33":"Anglais & fran\u00e7ais"},"ai":{"background":{"p":"L'ONU reconna\u00eet le r\u00f4le de la technologie, de la science et du renforcement des capacit\u00e9s comme piliers majeurs des moyens de mise en \u0153uvre et de r\u00e9alisation des ODD. \u00c0 l'\u00e9chelle mondiale, la r\u00e9volution de l'industrie 4.0 exige que les jeunes acqui\u00e8rent et entretiennent des comp\u00e9tences num\u00e9riques pour l'innovation et l'entrepreneuriat. En outre, le plan strat\u00e9gique Niger 2.0 cherche \u00e0 employer les technologies num\u00e9riques pour promouvoir le d\u00e9veloppement du Niger, en se concentrant sur quatre domaines strat\u00e9giques : l'administration en ligne, la promotion des comp\u00e9tences num\u00e9riques, un programme de villages intelligents et la cr\u00e9ation d'une ville d'innovation et de technologie. Ainsi, le programme Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence (BS-AI) est con\u00e7u pour combler le d\u00e9ficit de main-d'\u0153uvre en science-technologie-innovation (STI) et pour conduire l'agenda de transformation num\u00e9rique du Niger et de la r\u00e9gion du Sahel.","title":"Contexte"},"description":{"p":"Le programme Bachelor of Science in Artificial Intelligence - BS(AI) fournit aux apprenants les connaissances et les comp\u00e9tences n\u00e9cessaires pour transformer des entr\u00e9es complexes de texte, de vision, de langage et de grandes bases de donn\u00e9es en d\u00e9cisions intelligibles et exploitables pour am\u00e9liorer les capacit\u00e9s humaines. Le programme d'\u00e9tudes fournit une exp\u00e9rience pratique dans divers aspects de l'intelligence artificielle, y compris les fondements de la science des donn\u00e9es, les langages d'intelligence artificielle, l'apprentissage automatique, les r\u00e9seaux neuronaux artificiels et le d\u00e9veloppement de produits de donn\u00e9es soutenus par de solides bases de g\u00e9nie logiciel pour le web et le mobile, les principes agiles, l'\u00e9thique et la th\u00e9orie sociale. Le programme donnera aux \u00e9tudiants des comp\u00e9tences en mati\u00e8re de pens\u00e9e informatique, de mod\u00e9lisation des probl\u00e8mes, de g\u00e9nie logiciel et de gestion de projet pour d\u00e9velopper des syst\u00e8mes et des logiciels intelligents ax\u00e9s sur les donn\u00e9es afin de r\u00e9pondre aux probl\u00e8mes soci\u00e9taux et organisationnels dans les domaines de l'agriculture, du commerce, de l'\u00e9ducation, de la sant\u00e9, de l'industrie et de la gouvernance, etc.","title":"Description du programme"},"outcomes":{"p":{"1":"Tirer parti des principes de l'informatique en mettant l'accent sur l'intelligence artificielle pour r\u00e9soudre des probl\u00e8mes dans des domaines comme la sant\u00e9, l'\u00e9ducation, le commerce et l'agriculture, etc.","2":"Transformer des donn\u00e9es complexes, telles que la vision, le langage et d'autres bases de donn\u00e9es, en d\u00e9cisions intelligentes et exploitables.","3":"R\u00e9soudre les d\u00e9fis logiciels des applications et des syst\u00e8mes gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 un ensemble complet de comp\u00e9tences en ing\u00e9nierie logicielle dans les domaines du bureau, du web et du mobile.","4":"Appliquer des principes de leadership et d'\u00e9thique pour r\u00e9soudre des probl\u00e8mes soci\u00e9taux et organisationnels \u00e0 l'aide de l'IA."},"title":"R\u00e9sultats"},"title":" Intelligence artificielle"},"banner":"\u00c9tudier \u00e0 A.D.U.","ep":{"background":{"p":"The ADU English program is an English Learning establishment of the African Development University that is focused on building the English language proficiency of professionals, businessmen and businesswomen etc., especially in the francophone region and is committed to taking learners through an exciting language learning journey with courses tailored to give learners an all-round study of the language. A mastery of English language helps you to easily navigate through the business environment, to communicate effectively in English Language, collaborate effectively with English speaking colleagues, business partners and prospective business partners from English speaking countries and to increase your chances of getting jobs and expanding your net worth and network as a bilingual speaker.","title":"Background"},"cs":{"back":"Our syllabus is comprised of topics in English grammar, vocabulary and the four major language skills: listening, reading, writing, speaking. Our courses are delivered using the following methods: Teacher-led mode of instruction; Student-led mode of teaching: using debates, oral and written presentations etc. and Instructional video and audio materials.\\Students will take a placement test at the beginning of the program to determine their current proficiency level and at the end of the program, there will also be another placement test to review their growth rate. The current levels we have are Beginner (A1), Pre-intermediate (A2), Intermediate (B1) and High-intermediate (B2)","title":"Course Syllabus"},"packages":{"p":{"a":"<strong>On-Campus Package:<\/strong> We are located at Village de la Francophonie where our physical classes are held. Classes on campus take place every Tuesday and Thursday, 6:30pm.","b":"<strong>Company Package:<\/strong> We also have a learning package for companies and organizations who want members of their staff to learn English. Our teachers are available to come to your companies and teach based on the schedule that works for you. The only requirement for this package is for a class to have a minimum of 10 students\/learners."},"title":"Our Packages"},"title":"Programme d'anglais"},"majors":{"accounting":{"p1":"Un dipl\u00f4me en comptabilit\u00e9 et finance vous formera pour travailler comme examinateur financier, ou analyste financier, ou directeur financier ou comme consultant en affaires qui aide \u00e0 guider les petits entrepreneurs. C'est un travail tr\u00e8s exigeant... il n\u00e9cessite une grande attention aux d\u00e9tails.","p2":"Un dipl\u00f4me en comptabilit\u00e9 peut vous donner les comp\u00e9tences n\u00e9cessaires pour travailler comme consultant en entreprises et en finances, en aidant les entrepreneurs et les propri\u00e9taires de petites entreprises \u00e0 trouver la r\u00e9ussite financi\u00e8re.","title":"Baccalaur\u00e9at en comptabilit\u00e9"},"law":{"p1":"A.D.U. offre un dipl\u00f4me de trois ans en droit des affaires qui dispense des cours sur de nombreux aspects diff\u00e9rents du travail juridique. Les \u00e9tudiants qui s'inscrivent \u00e0 ce programme doivent avoir un fort engagement envers la justice et l'\u00e9galit\u00e9 et la lutte contre la corruption.","p2":"Les types de carri\u00e8res auxquels les dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s peuvent s'attendre sont les suivants : juriste d'entreprise, magistrat dans les juridictions publiques, consultant juridique, notaire public. Nos cours sont dispens\u00e9s par un groupe diversifi\u00e9 de professionnels qui apportent au campus de l'ADU une riche exp\u00e9rience internationale","title":"Licence en droit des affaires"},"mis":{"p1":"Les processus des technologies de l'information reposent sur la cr\u00e9ativit\u00e9 et la r\u00e9solution de probl\u00e8mes. Les \u00e9tudes en informatique vous donneront l'occasion d'utiliser vos comp\u00e9tences pour trouver des solutions innovantes aux probl\u00e8mes auxquels le monde est confront\u00e9.","p2":"Les postes disponibles en informatique comprennent souvent des emplois tels que la cr\u00e9ation de logiciels, l'analyse de nouvelles formes de donn\u00e9es et l'\u00e9laboration de solutions pour le monde hautement technologique d'aujourd'hui. Le programme d'A.D.U. vous placera au centre de ce domaine passionnant en vous formant \u00e0 la cr\u00e9ation de nouvelles technologies.","title":"Licence en syst\u00e8mes d'information de gestion"},"pm":{"p1":"Les gestionnaires de projet sont form\u00e9s pour s'assurer que les projets complexes se d\u00e9roulent conform\u00e9ment au calendrier. Les grandes organisations d'aide humanitaire telles que le HCR, le PAM et les ONG internationales emploient souvent de nombreux chefs de projet afin de maintenir l'efficacit\u00e9 des t\u00e2ches quotidiennes de l'organisation.","p2":"Conform\u00e9ment au concept Ilimi, chaque cours est con\u00e7u et enseign\u00e9 avec un fil conducteur de conduite \u00e9thique afin de renforcer la responsabilit\u00e9 des dipl\u00f4m\u00e9s \u00e0 faire pression sur les pratiques \u00e9thiques sur leur lieu de travail. Les cours mettent \u00e9galement l'accent sur l'engagement \u00e0 combattre l'injustice sociale et \u00e0 faire du monde un endroit meilleur pour les moins fortun\u00e9s.","title":"Licence en gestion de projet"},"title":"Administration des affaires (Majeures en vedette)"},"p":"L'Universit\u00e9 Africaine de D\u00e9veloppement (A.D.U) est une universit\u00e9 d'excellence bas\u00e9e \u00e0 Niamey (Niger). L'A.D.U s'inspire des plus grandes institutions mondiales d'enseignement sup\u00e9rieur telles que l'Universit\u00e9 d'Ashesi au Ghana et l'Universit\u00e9 de Harvard aux Etats-Unis. A.D.U est un \u00e9tablissement bilingue, avec un enseignement en fran\u00e7ais et en anglais.","title":"L'avantage de l'A.D.U."}}};